title: Crochet Sample Book (USA), late 19th century
inscribed: Tagged as a gift from "Vesta M. Stone, 275 Prospect St. Willimantic, Conn. to Roxa Wright, Needlework Editor, Woman's Day, Inc."
description: Oblong sample book of linen with 25 pages of samples of crochet worked in linen and cotton.

tombstone.epitaph: Crochet Sample Book (USA), late 19th century; linen, cotton; H x W: 25 x 20 cm (9 13/16 x 7 7/8 in.); Gift of Roxa Wright; 1957-130-9
